@node poo "AmiGreet ñ Freeware!"

 AmiGreet is freeware, you can send/copy/sell/eat/distribute it any way you want!

 I do ask that if you include it in a compilation pack or on a magazine CD-ROM or
 cover disk that you eMail me on gazy@globalnet.co.uk just to tell me so that I
 can buy the mag/disk/CD.

 *NOTE*

 You may have seen a similar program called 'Workbench Greet'. They say immitation
 is the best form of flattery.. well Im flattered that someone has taken the time
 to make a 'clone' of AmiGreet although I wasn't too happy to see that they were
 charging 10DM for an inferior version of AmiGreet!

@endnode
